+No action required. All acceptance criteria met, all hardening items either addressed in prior tasks (revise_score wiring, budget enforcement) or correctly scoped out (bootstrap_identity). The 25-combination mastering-policy verification test provides strong regression coverage for future cadence/phase additions.

